value: Siberia and Manchuria; winters to s China, Korea and Japan
Breeds from Transbaikalia and northwestern Mongolia east through Manchuria to Ussuriland. Winters in Korea and eastern China south to the Yangtse. Occurs in Japan on migration.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World
